SETUP INSTRUCTIONS


1) Ensure you have Ruby installed (>= 1.9.2) and SQLite3


2) Run the following to setup the environment:

    => gem install bundler
    => bundle


3) Launch the app from with:

    => rackup config.ru
    

Notes:
  * Each time the app is launched the database is wiped clean
  * Use `racksh` while the server is running to inspect the database contents
    (try it after a file has been successfully uploaded)